HEADWORD: Brachygrapher
<hw>Bra*chyg"ra*pher</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A writer in
short hand; a stenographer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He asked the <qex>brachygrapher</qex> whether he wrote the notes
of the sermon.</q> <rj><qau>Gayton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brachygraphy</ent>⟦br⟧
